citations:
    citation-agot-eddard-x:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Eddard X"
            text_from_source: "He dreamt an old dream, of three knights in white cloaks, and a tower long fallen, and Lyanna in her bed of blood."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Ned dreams of the Tower of Joy: three Kingsguard (Ser Arthur Dayne, Ser Oswell Whent, Ser Gerold Hightower) guarded a tower in the red mountains of Dorne; Ned's party of seven fought them. Ned wakes after six days unconscious. Robert and Cersei visit; Robert reinstates Ned as Hand. Key revelation: the Kingsguard were at the Tower of Joy, not at the Trident."
